`MachineWrapper` owns one embedded `{{ machine_class_name(model) }}` object. Use
`set_event_checks(...)` to mount the generated C poll event-check table before
calling `cycle()` on machines that declare events. Use `native_handle()` when
an existing C integration point needs the underlying handle.

